graph
=====

[ ] thick lines
[ ] no more than 3 information classes in one graph
[ ] error bars

[ ] big labels on x,y axes
[ ] for small numbers on log axis: 0.01 instead of -2

[ ] no resolution dependence!
[ ] if binned: number of bins such that trend visible, 20% "scattering" values max.

[ ] fits or other models where they exist

[ ] lots of data points not clustered as black area, but contour plot!
[ ] explain main statement in caption
[ ] explain errors in main text
[ ] constrain plotting area to region of confidence
[ ] exclude data generated by numerical effects
